      "text": "controller \n\nreq, res\n\nreq -> get data\n\nres-> what happened with\nthat data \n\nexample\nreq.body: give email and\npass to login \n\nverify : check that\ncredential are okay to\nlogin \n\nif yes \nstatus 200 that user\ncan login \n\nif user not exist \nerror 404 user not found ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "controller \n\nreq, res\n\nreq -> get data\n\nres-> what happened with that data \n\nexample\nreq.body: give email and pass to login \n\nverify : check that credential are okay to login \n\nif yes \nstatus 200 that user can login \n\nif user not exist \nerror 404 user not found ",
      "autoResize": false,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
