      "text": "routes\n\nrouters\nmiddleware include into api\nroutes\nasync wrap \n\nmain task of this \ndo api routing: switch\nbetween api and call\nspecific api which client\n(frontend) request\n\nadd middlewares\nadd test function\n(validations middlewares)",
