      "text": "main task\nset rate limiting\nset access limiting\nauthorization\nproducts or service\naccess to specific user\nonly\n\nexample\n\nGemeini give 5 video\ncreation per days, it rate\nlimit that you can\ngenerate only 5 vidoe in\nday\n\n\naccess limti\nnormal user -> can not\ntouch admin panel\n\n \nprimum version -> without\npurchase use na kari sake\n\n\n\n",
