      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "main task\nset rate limiting\nset access limiting\nauthorization\nproducts or service access to specific user only\n\nexample\n\nGemeini give 5 video creation per days, it rate limit that you can generate only 5 vidoe in day\n\n\naccess limti\nnormal user -> can not touch admin panel\n\n \nprimum version -> without purchase use na kari sake\n\n\n\n",
